
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Portal";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

@section CustomHead{ 
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/Content/Portals.css" />
}

<div class="well">
    <h2>Portals</h2>

    <p>Pazuzu Minecraft has a multiverse system.  There are portals located near the world spawn that will take you to one of four different locations.  The portal worlds get rotated regularly so please check back often for updates.</p>

    <p>The portals can be found at the following XYZ coordinates:<strong><font color="#809fff">-254, 80, 178</font></strong>.  Use the Map or the F3 key in game to see your current coordinates.</p>

    <!--Portal Row-->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1">
                    <div class="well" style="background-color: #ffccdd">
                        <h3><a href="http://www.planetminecraft.com/project/olann-island-contest-entry-wip/">Olann Island</a></h3>
                        <p>Explore Olann Island theme park and casino.  Water slides, rollercoasters, and a ferris wheel are all available from the pier, while a casino, heliport, and golf course are free to explore further inland. This map does not spawn mobs.</p>
                        <br />
                        <br />
                       

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-offset-5 col-sm-5">
                    <div class="well" style="background-color: #FFDD99">
                        <h3><a href="http://mc.jeremytoler.net/">Garangatang 2010</a></h3>
                        <p>Garangatangs very old server. This server was Damphons first experiance on minecraft. Explore a castle that will never be completed, and eat at the fabulous food bar. </p>
                        <br />
                        <br />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!--Portal Row-->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1">
                    <div class="well" style="background-color: #ffbf80">
                        <h3><a href="http://dev.bukkit.org/bukkit-plugins/cityworld/">Apocalyptica</a></h3>
                        <p>Challenge yourself to a night in Apocalyptica.  This metropolis is overrun by mobs- and not just any mobs.  The angry hordes swarming the city streets are stronger and more aggressive than standard Minecraft.  This portal also utilizes the Infernal Mobs Mod. This portal is on <strong>Hard</strong>.</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-offset-5 col-sm-5">
                   <div class="well" style="background-color: #d699ff">
                        <h3><a href="http://www.planetminecraft.com/project/the-hobbit---esgaroth-dale-erebor-amp-ravenhill/">Erebor</a></h3>
                        <p>A map inspired by The Hobbit.  Explore Laketown, Dale, and Erebor as they appeared in the Hobbit movies.  This portal is on <strong>Hard</strong> and Infernal Mobs can spawn.</p>
                        <br />
                       
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
 
</div>

